      How much is the train from Salem to North Station?
      Train or bus from Salem to North Station (subway)? The best way to get from Salem to North Station (subway) is to train which takes 42 min and costs $3 - $9. Alternatively, you can line 450 bus, which costs $1 - $5 and takes 1h 3m.
